# ==============================================================================
# ADMIN ACCOUNT
# ==============================================================================
# Used by seed_admin / create_admin / reset_admin to provision the admin user
# on container startup. If you change your password via the UI, also update
# ADMIN_PASSWORD here so re-runs of those scripts don't stomp the UI change.
